<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="about-us">
        <header>
            <h1>About Us</h1>
        </header>

        <!-- Introduction -->
        <section class="introduction">
            <h2>Introduction</h2>
            <p>The Doctors Web Forum platform was created to connect doctors worldwide, share knowledge, answer questions, and support critical cases. Our aim is to build a practical learning and working environment, helping doctors enhance their professional skills and exchange medical expertise.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- Objectives -->
        <section class="objectives">
            <h2>Project Objectives</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>To create an online discussion platform exclusively for doctors and medical professionals.</li>
                <li>To support the resolution of special and urgent medical cases through global connections.</li>
                <li>To provide a trustworthy environment for learning and sharing medical resources.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Problem Statement -->
        <section class="problem-statement">
            <h2>Problem Statement</h2>
            <p>Doctors often face challenges in exchanging ideas, supporting complex medical cases, or finding colleagues with the right expertise. Doctors Web Forum will serve as a bridge to help them connect, share, and assist each other more effectively.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- Deliverables -->
        <section class="deliverables">
            <h2>Key Features</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Register an account and manage personal information.</li>
                <li>An online forum that allows discussion of medical topics.</li>
                <li>Advanced search functionality by specialty and geographical location.</li>
                <li>Quick connections in emergency situations.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
